{
  "stem": "24106.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So first stop was in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There we celebrated Pesach, the first time after the war we celebrated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have a big Seder.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When were you able to observe the Jewish rituals after the war?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What was the first point that you felt free to--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came to-- when we stopped in Austria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- that was already-- that was already my home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went there, and then from there we went to-- we were climbing the Alps, and it was very, very [INAUDIBLE], because everything was illegal.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're not supposed to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything, you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The guard make believe they don't see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything was fixed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in the meantime you have to be alert.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, we stopped in Austria.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to Vienna, and they have a big place, it's called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was [INAUDIBLE] at [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you couldn't stay too long, because other people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was like a transit-- a transit place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So from there they took us to a smaller town, Linz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Over there in Linz was a big DP camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was about 2,000 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In most, the people-- there were Holocaust survivors, mostly from [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Katzett. ?] So my husband has a friend there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He get-- he got us-- it was like an apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Three rooms that we share.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Three families shared the room with a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we-- we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It wasn't so bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were-- this, it was the American zone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We  were in the [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Amerikanerzone. ?] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we got, you know-- they gave us-- so they-- they supported us by the UNRRA, by the Joint, and by the HAIS.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
